  <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="title:1;4:10">Introduction to CWRC-Writer Concepts</title>
  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:14">We have included overall concepts in our CWRC-Writer documentation as background
