    Relations/Triples. </shortdesc>
  <refbody class="- topic/body        reference/refbody " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="refbody:1;8:12">
    <section class="- topic/section " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="section:1;9:14">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="title:2;10:14">Introduction to CWRC-Writer</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="p:1;11:10">The Canadian Writing Research Collaboratory (CWRC) is developing an in-browser text markup
        editor (CWRC-Writer) for use by collaborative scholarly editing projects. </p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="p:2;13:10">Features of CWRC-Writer</p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="p:3;14:10">
        <ul id="ul_rch_vdc_zp" class="- topic/ul " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="ul:1;15:32">
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:1;16:15">Web based<ul id="ul_ep5_l2c_zp" class="- topic/ul " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="ul:2;16:47">
              <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:2;17:19">removes need to buy, install, and configure editing software</li>
              <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:3;18:19">based on TinyMCE, a JavaScript editor using jQuery to extend functionality</li>
            </ul></li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:4;20:15">Close-to-WYSIWYG editing and enrichment of scholarly texts with meaningful visual
            representational of markup</li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:5;22:15">Combines eXtensible Markup Language (XML) and Resource Description Framework (RDF).
              <ul id="ul_clc_52c_zp" class="- topic/ul " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="ul:3;23:38">
              <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:6;24:19">XML markup support crucial for DH community</li>
              <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:7;25:19">RDF increasingly in use in DH projects;supports standoff and overlapping
                annotation of named entities, notes, etc.</li>
              <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:8;27:19">ability to combine TEI markup with RDF for named entities and annotations.</li>
              <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:9;28:19">ability to export using "weavers" that recombine plain text, the XML, and the RDF
                (including TEI-compliant XML)</li>
            </ul></li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:10;31:15">Flexible Design<ul id="ul_kbw_cfc_zp" class="- topic/ul " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="ul:4;31:53">
              <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:11;32:19">can be dropped into existing web frameworks</li>
              <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:12;33:19">works with external services for e.g. entity management and validation</li>
              <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="li:13;34:19">documentation open-source (github) code allows adoption and modification.<image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A84a008e8-69be-4cd0-8d8d-fc8ffd62803f/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_k1t_pfc_zp" align="center" height="5in" width="5in" class="- topic/image " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="image:1;37:82"/><image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A495fd428-dbc3-48f9-8115-9aae4ac7fe08/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_bv1_1gc_zp" align="center" height="4in" width="6in" class="- topic/image " xtrf="/Users/ilovan/Documentation/CWRC-Writer/CWRCWriter_Concept_Splash.dita" xtrc="image:2;40:82"/></li>
            </ul></li>
        </ul>
      </p>
